data.description: Welcome to this spacious residence on a corner lot with stunning views of Pikes Peak and USAFA, proximity to Mary Kyer Park and Da Vinci Academy Elementary School. The main level of the house offers ample space, including a formal living area, formal dining room, kitchen, family room, a dedicated office, a half bath, and access to a beautiful patio. Upstairs, the primary suite stands out with its spaciousness, abundant natural light, window seats, vaulted ceilings, and a newly renovated attached bath with awesome double shower. Additionally, there are three more bedrooms and a shared full bathroom on this level. The basement is a versatile space that can accommodate multigenerational living or extended guests. One of the guest rooms in the basement is well-suited for use as an in-home gym or recreation room. There is plenty of room for additional living, games, or dining areas, ensuring that guests have ample space to spread out. The basement also features a convenient kitchenette with a full-size refrigerator. Completing the basement are an additional guest bedroom and a full bathroom. The location of this residence is highly appealing for those living in Northern Colorado Springs. It offers easy access to the Air Force Academy and a convenient commute to Denver. Shopping and dining options are just around the corner, featuring fantastic local shops. Mary Kyer Park is easily accessible, providing a picturesque setting for walks, dog-friendly activities, and outdoor play for children. The park features amenities such as a playground, tennis court, pond, waterfall, and basketball court. The area is well-known for its excellent schools, with the Da Vinci Academy elementary school within walking distance and visible from the back door. This wonderful home offers abundant space for growth, come see it today!
